::
++  get-light-charge
  |=  =charge
  ?.  ?=(%glob -.chad.charge)  charge
  charge(glob.chad *glob)
::  +ch: Charge engine
++  ch
  |_  =desk
  ++  pass  |=(=wire ~(. ^pass [%charge desk wire]))
  ++  glob-wire
    |=  glob-reference
    ^-  wire
    :+  %glob
      (scot %uv hash)
